# Input

```scss
@keyframes  loader{
#{50%-$loader-icon-duration}{opacity:1}
#{$i}%{opacity:.75}
50%,#{75%-$loader-icon-duration},to{opacity:.5}
entry 100%{opacity:1}
}

```


# Formatted

```scss
@keyframes loader {
	#{50% - $loader-icon-duration} {
		opacity: 1;
	}
	#{$i}% {
		opacity: 0.75;
	}
	50%,
	#{75% - $loader-icon-duration},
	to {
		opacity: 0.5;
	}
	entry 100% {
		opacity: 1;
	}
}

```
